


معماری:

```
اینترنت ── Azure Firewall ── ExpressRoute ── FortiGate On-Prem ── کاربران
              │
شبکه ملی ── AWS Network Firewall ── Direct Connect ── کاربران ملی
```

پیکربندی Azure Firewall (PowerShell):

```powershell
# ایجاد Rule Collection
$rule = New-AzFirewallNetworkRule -Name "AllowNational" -Protocol TCP `
    -SourceAddress "10.1.0.0/16" -DestinationAddress "192.168.1.0/24" `
    -DestinationPort 80,443

$ruleCollection = New-AzFirewallNetworkRuleCollection -Name "NationalRules" `
    -Priority 100 -Rule $rule -ActionType "Allow"

$azfw = Get-AzFirewall -Name "NationalFW"
$azfw.NetworkRuleCollections = $ruleCollection
Set-AzFirewall -AzureFirewall $azfw
```
